UNITED STATES OF AMERICA FEDERAL TRADE COMMISSION ________________________________________ In the Matter of ZALE CORPORATION, a corporation ________________________________________) The Federal Trade Commission has conducted an investigation of certain acts and practices of Zale Corporation, a corporation ("proposed respondent").
Proposed respondent, having been represented by counsel, is willing to enter into an agreement containing a consent order resolving the allegations contained in the attached draft complaint.
Therefore, IT IS HEREBY AGREED by and between Zale Corporation, by its duly authorized officers, and counsel for the Federal Trade Commission that: 1.
